{"tid":2318114,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"因信賴而聽的 (G)I-DLE 即將回歸！距離〈DUMDi DUMDi〉不到半年","createTime":"2020-12-09T05:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T07:32:02.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0d3506de85e68742d520cefbe9faebfff9f5b8d6","tid":2318114,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_1eaed8003bfc02e4a763e9942c9aa9d8/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-09/132193-888191.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_1eaed8003bfc02e4a763e9942c9aa9d8%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-09%2F132193-888191.png&h=795da61a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n時隔短短五個月，(G)I-DLE 便將再度帶著新作品回歸，很期待不斷推陳出新的她們這次又會端出什麼樣的新作品！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCUBE Entertainment 今天（8 日）透露 (G)I-DLE 正在準備新專輯，預訂於 2021 年 1 月回歸歌壇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_351fb131b9ca88f8c7ec7668b4c72584/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-09/132193-888189.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_351fb131b9ca88f8c7ec7668b4c72584%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-09%2F132193-888189.jpeg&h=0857cf4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每次都帶著自創曲展開活動的 (G)I-DLE，自出道以來始終維持著穩定的回歸步調。例如她們在去年 3 月發行第三張迷你專輯〈I trust〉，8 月又推出充滿夏日風情的單曲〈DUMDi DUMDi〉，而距離下次回歸也僅有五個月。<br />\n<br />\n特別的是，去年 (G)I-DLE 在發行〈I trust〉的同時，和美國唱片公司 republic records 簽了約，也讓她們接下來在國際上的表現更受矚目。在迎接 (G)I-DLE 的新作品前，就先回味她們最近在《2020 MAMA》上的精彩表演吧！"},{"pid":"843656e54ccfbf7f37f0322d787aa3bb06a05b6a","tid":2318114,"uid":256796,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:55:03.000Z","msg":"YQDD<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993f395b1de3b64d23ec3d3bb90797baa20de05d","tid":2318114,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"843656e54ccfbf7f37f0322d787aa3bb06a05b6a","tid":2318114,"uid":256796,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-